Dialogs.Dialog: Well... What do you think about kissing, ▲小早川＊▲？
！？ Why do you ask all of a sudden...？
Well, sometimes I just wonder if I'm being pushy...
If I force you to do it, that wouldn't be good...
For some certain thing, being forced a little bit isn't really too bad...
But this is too bad. Head banging！
(I have to be careful about this...)
Well... What do you think about kissing, ▲小早川＊▲？
For example... Well... You like it... Or you don't like it...
...I don't care much. When I want to do it, I'll do it.
Sometimes I'm afraid that you might not like it when I kiss you...
But, that's... There are a lot of factors to it, you know...
But if it's obvious that you care about Rinko, you can do it anytime...
(It's so hard to please you ▲小早川＊▲...)
Well... What do you think about kissing, ▲小早川＊▲？
It's... Sometimes I wonder that I might force you.
You didn't force me, but... When you kiss me all of a sudden, that scares me a little bit.
I also have to apologize to you, okay？ I'll try not to be scared.
Well... What do you think about kissing, ▲小早川＊▲？
What！？ What are you saying？ Are you an idiot...？
...Nothing in particular. It's just normal, okay？
Okay. Normal, huh...？ You like normal kisses then ▲小早川＊▲...
Me？ W-Well, since I'm older, kissing is just something... natural.
I don't even know that you were such a pervert. ...Don't get close to me.
Hey... I have a question ▲主人公＊▲.
Well, why do you kiss Rinko...？
Love to kiss？ Or love Rinko？
Eh？ Ah, I love to kiss but it's actually because the one I'm kissing is you, ▲小早川＊▲.
I see... Then I have another question.
What if... Well... What if Rinko is the one to kiss you？ Would you feel bad...？
I wouldn't feel bad... Eh？ Don't tell me you want to kiss me... now？
Hey... I have a question ▲主人公＊▲.
Hey, when do you feel like kissing Rinko？
！？ Well, hmm... When I suddenly think that you're cute.
It seems to be pure libido then.
Whatever. Well, this is like a 1/10000 chance. Like 99.99% it'd never happen.
What if... Rinko is the one to kiss you？ Will you think of Rinko as a bad girl？
Hey... I have a question ▲主人公＊▲.
Well... When do you feel like you want to kiss Rinko？
！？ Well, hmm... There are different situations...
Rinko actually can tell, you know？ When you're about to kiss Rinko...
Well, can you tell when Rinko wants to be kissed ▲主人公＊▲？
You can't tell, right？ Well, maybe I should make it easier for you to understand.
What do you think about love ▲小早川＊▲？
That's... Why do you always ask such embarrassings questions？ For me, it's normal...
Well... But it's good that we discuss about this occasionally, right？
I don't really know. This is my first time to be in love. But....
Are you happy to be with Rinko？ Is your heart throbbing？
Me, too. My heart always throbs when we're together. Sometimes it's scary.
I still don't know anything much, but that's how I feel.
What do you think about love ▲小早川＊▲？
What？ What did you say？ Are you an idiot？
W-Well. This is important for our relationship, you know？
Not really. It doesn't really matter, does it？
Even if our relationship fails, it still doesn't matter to you？
Eh...？ No. I didn't mean it that way.
But it can't be helped. Sometimes I even feel like I'm not myself...
So, it just can't be helped！ This is too troublesome！
What do you think about love ▲小早川＊▲？
W-Well, this is a little embarrassing, but it's important to us, right？
I see... But I don't really know. It's my first time to be someone's girlfriend.
Rinko loves you too. Is it okay that Rinko will ask you this question again later？
Thanks. For Rinko, this much is already enough.
What would your ideal situation be if someone confessed his love to you, ▲小早川＊▲？
What？ Are you playing some dating simulation games？
Well, since I'm a guy, I'm concerned about it, you know？
Hey, what would your ideal situation be？
Well, if he's handsome, smart and mature, he'd meet my requirements, and...
Ah, no. I wonder if it's something like this.
Shut up！ Get away from me！
What do you think about love ▲小早川＊▲？
I was asked this question before, so I have been thinking about it.
But, I really don't know. It's just...
Rinko is in love now, ▲主人公＊▲.
The feeling is different from what I read from books. It's different from any feelings I have ever had...
It's something nobody has taught me, but I knew it that I was already in love. It's just mysterious.
What do you think about love ▲小早川＊▲？
I was asked this question before. That's why I've been thinking about it.
When I'm with you, I feel embarrassed, happy and nervous. And these feelings are overwhelming.
But you're always so cool and calm. You make Rinko feel like an idiot, ▲主人公＊▲.
But I'm not calm. Not at all.
I feel bad for being like that when I'm with you... But I feel even worse when I'm away from you.
I feel so lonely when I can't see you...
Sorry. Rinko is just so troublesome for you. Thank you for being with Rinko.
What do you think about love ▲小早川＊▲？
You've asked me this before, right？ I've been thinking about it and I finally realized.
Yeah. Realized that Rinko is really in love.
Sometimes you say that you love Rinko, right, ▲主人公＊▲？
And I'm always happy to hear that. It's like we've confirmed our feelings.
I always lack confidence. Soon after that, I'll start to feel insecure, and that is painful.
But when you say you love me again, I can feel something warm inside my heart. I can feel your love.
That why it's obvious that Rinko is in love with you.
When do you feel jealous, ▲小早川＊▲？
Well... Don't you ever feel jealous at all？ We're dating, right？
For example, if I become popular among girls...
Ask me again when you become popular then.
Do you think you're the jealous type, ▲小早川＊▲？
Rinko？ You think Rinko is jealous？
Tsk... Since when did Rinko ever get jealous？
Never is never！ Are you an idiot？
Do you think you're the jealous type ▲小早川＊▲？
Jealous？ Rinko won't get jealous, so you can rest assured. Rinko trusts you.
Yeah. That you will only lay your eyes on Rinko.
Even though you sometimes glance at some girls while we're on our dates.
Do you think you're the jealous type ▲小早川＊▲？
Really？ But girls usually get jealous, right？
Sort of. Some girls in my class are like that.
And they'd scream "No, no！ You have to look at me only！" Something like that...
Oh！ That was nice！ Do it again！
N-o！！ Geez... You're an idiot. Idiot！
(You don't have to get that mad at me...)
When do you feel jealous ▲小早川＊▲？
Didn't we talk about this before？
I might be very jealous, but I don't know about that.
I know that I usually don't have confidence in myself. That's why you should make me feel more confident...
For that... You already knew it.
Do you think you're the jealous type, ▲小早川＊▲？
Again... Let me tell you. I'll never get jealous. Never ever！
Then what if I fall in love with another girl？
Eh！？ No, it was just for an example！
Even if it's just an example, you're so cruel to say something like that...
As a punishment, one month from now, you're prohibited to talk with any girl except Rinko.
Do you think you're the jealous type, ▲小早川＊▲？
We talked about this before, right？
Actually, there are times that I can't really take it. I'm not very confident in myself, you know.
So, when Rinko feels really insecure, you should come to Rinko...
And say that you love Rinko.
(That's it...？ I'll have to take this seriously.)
What do you think about skinship？
Can't you do it in a smarter way？ Rinko is a girl, after all.
Got it. I'll hone my skills.
(What do you want me to do then...？)
What do you think about skinship？
You seem to think about something perverted.
You are！ Yes, you absolutely are！
Okay. So, from now on, I'll refrain from touching you...
So, you're not gonna touch me！？ You idiot！
(What do you want me to do then...？)
What do you think about skinship？
No. I mean... I'm afraid that you might hate it.
I don't hate it. I'm happy about it, but...
You're still not very good at it.
What do you think about skinship？ Like, when the lovers touch each other and stuff...
No！ I didn't mean it in a perverted way. It's natural for people who are dating, right？
Well, lovers can do what they want. If the other party doesn't object.
I see. Then... How about you, ▲小早川＊▲？
Rinko's boyfriend will have to be able to withstand something like that.
What do you think about skinship？
R-Really...？ Then you must hate it, right？
I didn't say I hate it. Actually, I'm happy about it, but...
Just don't stare at me with those sparkling eyes！
What do you think about skinship？ Like, when the lovers touch each other and stuff...
But I can handle it better than before. If it's not too extreme, I can allow that.
If I don't like it, I'll let you know... with a kick.
What do you think about skinship？
Well... I'm afraid that you might hate it.
No, I think you've tuned yourself to my pace. I'm happy about it.
Really！？ Then I'll keep honing my skills！
Somehow, you eyes are so sparkling, huh？
